### ========================================
### TESTING OFFERS
### ========================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### ========================================
### 1. LOGIN (get JWT token)
### ========================================
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

