### 14. CREATE OFFER WITH INSUFFICIENT IMAGES (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/offers
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Cozy apartment in Paris",
  "description": "Beautiful apartment with Eiffel Tower view.",
  "city": "Paris",
  "previewImage": "apartment-1.jpg",
  "images": ["apartment-1.jpg", "apartment-2.jpg"],
  "isPremium": true,
  "type": "apartment",
  "rooms": 2,
  "guests": 4,
  "price": 150,
  "goods": ["Breakfast"],
  "host": "698deb8418032e5703fd15df",
  "location": {
    "latitude": 48.8566,
    "longitude": 2.3522
  }
}

###

### 15. GET NON-EXISTENT OFFER (should return 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/offers/000000000000000000000000
